email.js
- you will find a function sendMail where you have to update SMTP to send mails to users.
- Domain, username and password needs to be updated

db.js
- in this file you have connectWithDb function, you will have to update the connectiion string.

chat.js
- this file contains openai API_KEY which I have added of my own you need to replace that.

user.js
- In this file you need to search "forgot-password" you will see router.post in this you will have to update the resetLink which you will see localhost for now.